---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="SmartBrain AI - Intelligent Code Analysis">
  <main>
    <div class="hero">
      <h1 class="neo-text-glow">üß† <span class="text-gradient">SmartBrain AI</span></h1>
      <p class="tagline">Advanced AI-powered code analysis and automation</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="neo-card feature-card neo-glow-primary">
        <div class="feature-icon">üîç</div>
        <h3>Code Analysis</h3>
        <p>Deep learning-powered code analysis to detect patterns, vulnerabilities, and optimization opportunities in your smart contracts.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="neo-card feature-card neo-glow-accent">
        <div class="feature-icon">ü§ñ</div>
        <h3>Automated Workflows</h3>
        <p>Intelligent automation of repetitive tasks, from code generation to deployment pipelines, powered by advanced AI models.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="neo-card feature-card neo-glow-secondary">
        <div class="feature-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
        <h3>Security Intelligence</h3>
        <p>Real-time threat detection and vulnerability assessment using machine learning trained on millions of code samples.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="capabilities">
      <h2 class="section-title">AI Capabilities</h2>
      
      <div class="capability-list">
        <div class="neo-glass capability-item">
          <div class="capability-header">
            <span class="capability-icon">‚ö°</span>
            <h3>Smart Contract Generation</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Generate secure, optimized smart contracts from natural language descriptions. SmartBrain understands Solidity, Rust, and other blockchain languages.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="neo-glass capability-item">
          <div class="capability-header">
            <span class="capability-icon">üìä</span>
            <h3>Predictive Analytics</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Predict potential issues, gas optimization opportunities, and security vulnerabilities before deployment using AI-powered pattern recognition.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="neo-glass capability-item">
          <div class="capability-header">
            <span class="capability-icon">üîÑ</span>
            <h3>Automated Refactoring</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Intelligently refactor code for better performance, readability, and maintainability while preserving functionality and security.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="neo-glass capability-item">
          <div class="capability-header">
            <span class="capability-icon">üéØ</span>
            <h3>Conflict Resolution</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Automatically resolve merge conflicts in complex codebases using context-aware AI that understands code semantics and project structure.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-section">
      <div class="neo-card cta-card">
        <h2>Get Started with SmartBrain</h2>
        <p>Deploy SmartBrain AI in your development workflow today</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/docs/quickstart" class="neo-button neo-glow-primary">Quick Start Guide</a>
          <a href="/operators" class="neo-button">Operator Console</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    margin: auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
  }

  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .text-gradient {
    background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--neo-primary), var(--neo-accent));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.3rem);
    color: #666;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .feature-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .capabilities {
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
    color: var(--neo-primary);
  }

  .capability-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .capability-item {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: all var(--transition-medium);
  }

  .capability-item:hover {
    transform: translateX(10px);
    border-color: var(--neo-primary);
  }

  .capability-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .capability-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .capability-item h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .capability-item p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cta-section {
    margin: 4rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .cta-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--glass-bg), rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.05));
  }

  .cta-card h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .cta-card p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #666;
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .neo-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  /* Mobile responsiveness */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .feature-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .cta-card {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .neo-button {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
